''' ({{lang-ru|\u0414\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0441 \u0410\u043b\u0435\u043a\u0441\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447 \u0411\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0448\u0430\u043a\u043e\u0432}}; born 7 June 1987) is a [[Russia]]n professional [[Association football|football]]er.\n\n==Club career==\nHe made his debut in the [[Russian Premier League]] in 2007 for [[FC Luch-Energiya Vladivostok]].<ref name=career>{{FootballFacts.ru|13670<!-- -bolshakov-denis-aleksandrovich -->}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bolshakov, Denis}}\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:People from Kasimov]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Russian footballers]]\n[[Category:Russia youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Russian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in France]]\n[[Category:FC Dynamo Moscow reserves players]]\n[[Category:FC Luch Vladivostok players]]\n[[Category:Russian Premier League players]]\n[[Category:FC Torpedo Moscow players]]\n[[Category:FC SKA-Khabarovsk players]]\n[[Category:FC Oryol players]]\n[[Category:FC Lokomotiv Moscow players]]\n[[Category:Saif Sporting Club players]]\n[[Category:Bangladesh Football Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Bangladesh]]\n\n\n{{Russia-footy-midfielder-1987-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Russian professional footballer|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name= Denis Bolshakov\n| fullname = Denis Aleksandrovich Bolshakov\n| image =\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|1987|6|7|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = [[Kasimov]], [[Russian SFSR]]\n| height = {{height|m=1.82}}\n| currentclub  = \n| clubnumber = \n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n| youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = \n| years1  = 2004\u20132005 | clubs1  = [[OGC Nice]] (B team)            | caps1  =  1 | goals1  =  0 \n| years2  = 2005      | clubs2  = [[FC Lokomotiv Moscow]]          | caps2  =  0 | goals2  =  0\n| years3  = 2006      | clubs3  = [